				<li>Has a higher chance to perform ghost events shattering the lights</li>
				<li>Can turn off a light instantly if a player turns on a light within 4 metres of the ghost
					<ul>
						<li>Each light has a minimum cooldown per player of 10 seconds after it has been turned on or off</li>
						<li>Interacting with a light before the cooldown ends restarts it</li>
						<li>This ability does not work if the lights are already shattered</li>
					</ul>
				</li>
			</ul>
